All brick well constructed large two story Baltis built Georgian in Westchester.  Easy access to major highways, downtown, O'hare and Midway.  Beautiful hardwood floors throughout.  Updated Kitchen and Basement.  Recently repainted.  Large deck recently refinished.

Neighborhood Description

Quiet family neighborhood.  Close to park and community tennis courts.  Near community swimming pool.
data.whatILove: Solid construction with little upkeep required.  Separate laundry area in basement with large basin.  Large backyard with fence and garden area.
